{"tid":1515943,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民間記者會︰蒙面法針對示威者不合理","createTime":"2019-08-29T11:14:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T14:55:03.000Z","uid":60545,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"75f7534cda287c69115828f5f9e934b1614f1050","tid":1515943,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:14:30.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】反修例人士舉行民間記者會，表明不會參與行政長官林鄭月娥提出建立的對話平台。<br />\n<br />\n民間記者會發言人稱，林鄭月娥表明不接受五大訴求並考慮引用緊急法，批評林鄭月娥並非想真誠對話，只是一場閉門公關騷，認為雙方不存在對話空間，又指林鄭月娥過往曾就皇后碼頭爭議、利東街重建項目以及2014年政改與市民進行三次對話，事實反映對話後政府仍然無視市民意見，甚至有參與者遭政治清算，因此不打算參與對話。<br />\n<br />\n對於有政黨提出訂立蒙面法禁止遮蓋面容，發言人認為針對示威者不合理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=360927&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D360927%26refer%3D&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRkpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=ccd97a57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D360927%26refer%3D&h=e5488455\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=360927&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"2ebd593c43abf9794d2e1a58c4b90f1dd03bd9bb","tid":1515943,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:15:42.000Z","msg":"Winter on fire 2.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結局係點<br />\n大家都知啦"},{"pid":"7a6631eb865af1b5fe27780b31d38d87da15972f","tid":1515943,"uid":265662,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:16:38.000Z","msg":"我要委任證呀"},{"pid":"bf5e9a56d878797a150afec40bd74a116b26c799","tid":1515943,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:17:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"415b5812f24e41730d65e877dd1965904d30f629","tid":1515943,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:17:39.000Z","msg":"<im